1.text: The windblast creates a cascading shockwave across any River or Brush it passes through, as well as around the borders of Terrain it reaches, dealing physical damage to enemies hit,  stunning them for 0.5 − 1 (based on proximity) seconds, and briefly granting  sight of the area along its path.
